channel.title: Illegal Start of Expression
channel.description:
[code]client.java:21499: illegal start of expression public boolean ResetAttack() { ^ 1 error Press any key to continue . . .[/code]
How can I fix this? I have tried removing and adding brackets in the code before it, but that only changes the error to a different one.[br][size=1]Posted on: January 01, 2007, 08:00:13 PM[/size][hr]Hm well...
